#### 建议 2: 完善 BaseAgent 历史记录管理 🟡

**问题**: `fullHistory` 无限增长可能导致内存溢出

**建议方案**:

```typescript
// base-agent.ts 改进
export abstract class BaseAgent {
  private maxFullHistoryLength: number = 1000; // 最大历史记录数
  private historyPersistenceEnabled: boolean = true;

  /**
   * 优化后的保存历史方法，增加大小限制
   */
  private saveHistoryToFile(): void {
    if (!this.historyFile) return;

    try {
      // 限制历史记录大小
      if (this.fullHistory.length > this.maxFullHistoryLength) {
        this.fullHistory = this.fullHistory.slice(-this.maxFullHistoryLength);
      }

      const fs = require('fs');
      const dir = path.dirname(this.historyFile);

      if (!fs.existsSync(dir)) {
        fs.mkdirSync(dir, { recursive: true });
      }

      // 压缩存储
      fs.writeFileSync(
        this.historyFile,
        JSON.stringify(this.fullHistory, null, 2),
        'utf-8'
      );
    } catch (err) {
      // 记录错误但不中断主流程
      console.error('Failed to save history:', err);
    }
  }

  /**
   * 清理过期历史记录
   */
  public cleanupHistory(olderThanDays: number = 7): void {
    const cutoffDate = new Date();
    cutoffDate.setDate(cutoffDate.getDate() - olderThanDays);

    this.fullHistory = this.fullHistory.filter(
      entry => new Date(entry.timestamp) > cutoffDate
    );
  }
}
```

